column2: Monkberry is a JavaScript library for building web user interfaces

column5:
Merge pull request #55 from Abdillah/master

Add multiline comment support
Fix bug on loops with condition combination.

Merge pull request #30 from Madumo/fix_no_cache

Truly disable cache when noCache option is set to true

Merge pull request #21 from tuliot/master

Updated README.md; fixed typo
Update views of loops with options only once in onUpdate callback.
Fix bug with custom tag importing.
Fix bug with loop options cache.

Merge pull request #13 from ddoria921/ddoria921-patch-1

Update README.md
Add Object, Array, JSON as globals.
Throw Error object instead of strings in querySelector.
Refactor transforms from object to array.
Add context feature and fix this reference for nested templates.
Refactor Monkberry way of updating nested views.
Refactor updaters to spots. No more complex updaters. Less call stack.
Refactor figure, rename updaters to spots.
Add more regression tests to cover previous bugs.
Refactor custom tags to use complex caching updater.
Fix bug with updating local variables.
Migrate from λ.* to λ__* complex updater function names.
Separate regression test from monkberry spec.
Add some test for getElementById and querySelector. Fix getElementById algorithm.

Merge pull request #1 from XXXVII/master

Added support for Opera 12.16 in querySelector.
Added support for Opera 12.16 in querySelector.
Update parser version to match new way of versioning.
Fix very sophisticated bug with local variables.
Add comments, rename dom() into createDocument(), remove onUpdate trigger.
Add test for attrs without quotes.
Fix temple for syntax. Add test for this.
Do not use matches on PhantomJS.
Fix spec and add boolean default attr values.
Back to separate methods for render.
Add onRemove to list of views methods.
Separate render function on user/internal. Add force remove.
Get template name from full file path.
Add result var to generated code.
Add more tests. Fix object iterating.
Improve performance. Remove double updating. Fix possible DX with "if" tags. Better source maps.
Add extra test for updating nested views. Fix trimming whitespace.
Optimize update for "ForStatement" then no "key, value" specified.
Implement complex data updates for nested views.
Add SVG and Custom tag support. Add trimming of whitespaces.
